<paragraph id="A4C0E23CD1D3B649BE50637B95A9CB5F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
ARGENTINA. Misiones, 
<emphasis id="CE6F3E7B338F4BEE187FF7A382819075" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">G.J. Schwarz</emphasis>
5098 (lectotype LIL001225, designated here; isolectotypes LIL, P).
